{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MS03_160.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1c,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x206,
            "name_id": 0x20,
            "extra_id": 0x22f,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Oink moo."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Huh...? Poro! What are you doing here?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x206,
            "name_id": 0x20,
            "extra_id": 0x22f,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Oink moo. Oink moo moo!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "If Poro is here, then does that mean Nanaca is around here, too?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I knew it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x1a1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha! Thank goodness, I was looking for you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Huh? For me?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Yup. Poro and I split up to find you.<CR>I had a feeling you were here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Whoa...Poro can even go on manhunts..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Oh, what did you want with me?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x46,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Hehe, I came here to help with my brother's shop, but now that that's done..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x47,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I was hoping to check out the bazaar with you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Oh, good idea! Shopping with you sounds fun!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x48,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Right? I'd feel more comfortable going with you, as you're accustomed to the city."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x35,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, if anything, I'm a country gal, too..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "And then, I was hoping you could stop me from whittling away all my money."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Wh-What do you mean by that?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x11a,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Well, so...I take everything that the shop person says seriously..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x11b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "And if I'm told that something is a good item, I believe it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x11e,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "But when I think it over a little while later, I find that I have lots of items that I didn't necessary need..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I can kind of see that..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x11f,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "I wonder if I'm not good with dealing with pushy people...but my brother gets mad at me for wasting my money..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x120,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "So if you're here with me, I'll feel more at ease!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "I-I'm also, if anything, weak to getting pushed around, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x21e,
            "name_id": 0x5b,
            "extra_id": 0x206,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Hey there ladies, I have some nice accessories! Come take a look."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Uh-oh, here it comes. What should we do, Ayesha?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "U-Unless it's something we really need, we should have the courage and say no."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xe,
            "name_id": 0xe,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Okay. Ayesha, we can do this together...!"
        }
    ]
}